  "remarks": "\nSaad Sazeh Faraz Sharif is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: Saad Sazeh Faraz Sharif is or has been involved in hostile activity by the Government of Iran by carrying on business in the Iranian defence sector, specifically the manufacture of components for unmanned aerial vehicles. \n",
